Package com.ryanantkowiak.jOptionsHouseAPI

Class Summary
IOh Base class for other classes that wrap functionality for communication with OptionsHouse API.
JsonUtilities Collection of static utility methods for using JSON strings and objects.
OhAccountActivity This class will retrieve the Account Activity from OptionsHouse
OhAccountDetails This class will retrieve the Account Details from OptionsHouse.
OhAccountList This class will retrieve the list of accounts from OptionsHouse
OhAccountPositions This class will retrieve the Positions associated with an account from OptionsHouse
OhAllOrderStatus This class will retrieve the status of all orders from an OptionsHouse account
OhCancelOrder This class manages the cancellation of an OptionsHouse order
OhKeepAlive This class will send a session KeepAlive request to OptionsHouse.
OhLogin This class will log into the OptionsHouse API.
OhLogout This class will log out of the OptionsHouse API
OhOrderDetails This class will retrieve the details about one order at OptionsHouse.
OhOrderHistory This class will retrieve history events associated with one order from OptionsHouse.
OhQuote This class will retrieve quote pricing data from OptionsHouse for a security or list of securities.
OhSimpleOrder This class will create a simple one-legged order on OptionsHouse
OhViewSeries This class will retrieve the list of option security symbols for a provided underlying stock symbol, from OptionsHouse.
OptionsHouseUtilities This class contains some utility methods that are useful when dealing with OptionsHouse symbols and keys.
 

Enum Summary
PositionType Enumeration of the types of positions in an OptionsHouse account.
Side Enumeration of the side of an OptionsHouse order (Buy-side or Sell-side)
TimeInForce Enumerates the Time In Force values that can be attributed to an order on OptionsHouse
